    Motif cases for matching a List with cons.

    An extractor for extracting a List with a single element.

    An extractor for extracting a List into a head element and a tail of remaining elements.
    ListConsNilExtractor<A>
    An extractor for extracting an empty list.
    OptionalCases
    Motif cases for matching an Optional.
    OptionalExtractor<T>
    An extractor for extracting an Optional.
    OptionalFieldExtractor<T>

    OptionalNoneExtractor<T>
    An extractor for extracting an empty Optional.
    OptionalNoneFieldExtractor<T>
    A field extractor for extracting the value in an empty Optional.
